<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4496344>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 14. A–E: Maladera perniciosa (Brenske, 1898) (Vietnam: Lao Cai: Sa Pa); F–J: M. sontica (Brenske, 1898) (Laos: Louangnamtha: Namtha); K–O: M. verticalis (Fairmaire, 1888b) (China: Shaanxi: Houzhenzi). A, F, K: aedeagus, left side lateral view; D, I, N: aedeagus, right side lateral view; B, G, L: aedeagus, dorsal view; C, H, M: left parameres, ventral view; E, J, O: habitus. Scale: 0.5 mm. Habitus not to scale." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4496344/files/figure.png" .

